text: Juhana Aho (born September 30, 1993) is a Finnish professional ice hockey goaltender currently playing for Jukurit of the Liiga.Profile at Jatkoaika.com Aho made his Liiga debut for Jukurit during the 2017–18 Liiga season.Profile at Liiga.fi He previously played in the Mestis for Jukurit as well as JYP- Akatemia, SaPKo and Imatran Ketterä.Juhana Aho with Ketterä for the End of the Season (in Finnish) He also had a spell in the Erste Bank Eishockey Liga (EBEL) in Austria in 2019 for Dornbirner EC.Juhana Aho Walks to the EBEL League (in Finnish) ==References== ==External links== * Category:1993 births Category:Living people Category:Dornbirn Bulldogs players Category:Finnish ice hockey goaltenders Category:JYP-Akatemia players Category:Imatran Ketterä players Category:Mikkelin Jukurit players Category:Sportspeople from Jyväskylä Category:SaPKo players
